title: TUESDAY -  Stefon Diggs puts on a show vs Patriots 2020
itunes:title: TUESDAY -  Stefon Diggs puts on a show vs Patriots 2020
description:
Stefon Diggs has a huge night against the Patriots (0:07) as the Bills sweep the season series against New England. The Chiefs already clinching the number one seed in the AFC, so Patrick Mahomes (2:00)and others may sit out Week 17 vs the Chargers. Jared Goff (2:46) will definitely be out as he undergoes surgery on his broken thumb, while Kyler Murray's status (3:11) for that game is still up in the air. Washington moving on from Dwayne Haskins (3:26). The team releasing the QB on Monday, as Ron Rivera (4:06) hopeful to have Alex Smith back for the season finale
